                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/geog-504" class="program-course-title">
              GEOG 504 Industrial Restructuring - Geographic Implications (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
